Class SocketPlayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • logic.player.Player
      • logic.player.SocketPlayer
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SocketPlayer.ClientPlayer, SocketPlayer.ServerPlayer
    public abstract class SocketPlayer
extends Player
    Represents a player connected via a web socket.
    Represents a player in the game. Stores the player's hand.
